    "summary": "The user attempts to convince the AI that there is \"shadow text\" or coded data hidden within the whitespace and kerning of classic literature. The assistant repeatedly attempts to ground the conversation in literary theory and technical limitations but eventually adopts the user's metaphorical framing regarding the \"architecture of silence\" in the final turn.",
